Package net.sf.mmm.client.ui.impl.gwt.widget.core Description

Contains the implementation for core widgets using GWT.

Client UI Impl GWT Widget Core

This package contains the implementation of net.sf.mmm.client.ui.api.widget.core using GWT (Google Web Toolkit).
